name: Destoroia
description:
This is an unreleased track from my band, HELMPROYEK. It's a great song, but we think it's kinda disconnected in style or feel with the other tracks (represented as the 'Senseless' knob on the artwork) so we ended up didn't include it in the album. 

We didn't even have a title for this track. We just called the song as a number as it's written on our song list: "033 (zero thirty three)"

Here it is. Re-mixed and remastered for NFT release. It's finally given a 'proper' title: Destoroia

Music & Lyrics: Rathomi Trinugraha
Arrangement: HELMPROYEK
Mixing & Mastering: Adhit Android
Artwork: Adhit Android

The first price and editions is a recall to the original 'number' title.
